365
00:18:38,110 --> 00:18:39,630
My child is gone.

366
00:18:40,310 --> 00:18:41,960
My wife is gone.

367
00:18:42,510 --> 00:18:43,240
Mom...

368
00:18:43,240 --> 00:18:44,830
Why did you have to take Little Spud

369
00:18:44,830 --> 00:18:46,511
