416
00:21:01,590 --> 00:21:04,150
♪Searching day after day♪

417
00:21:04,160 --> 00:21:05,830
What should I do?

418
00:21:05,830 --> 00:21:09,460
♪For the person you used to be♪

419
00:21:09,660 --> 00:21:13,090
♪The night stretches on♪

420
00:21:13,340 --> 00:21:16,520
