478
00:23:45,960 --> 00:23:47,160
Please give me back my child.

479
00:23:47,160 --> 00:23:48,310
Give me back my baby!

480
00:23:48,310 --> 00:23:50,133
If you bought the child,
it's still illegal.

481
00:23:50,155 --> 00:23:52,177
