500
00:24:24,550 --> 00:24:25,466
Stop talking nonsense.

501
00:24:25,466 --> 00:24:26,270
Please help me!

502
00:24:26,270 --> 00:24:27,240
Don't talk nonsense.

503
00:24:27,550 --> 00:24:28,480
Folks, listen up,

504
00:24:28,590 --> 00:24:29,510
