505
00:24:30,000 --> 00:24:31,240
This child was abducted.

506
00:24:31,240 --> 00:24:32,240
We're taking him back.

507
00:24:32,240 --> 00:24:32,920
Please make way.

508
00:24:32,920 --> 00:24:34,440
