534
00:25:21,350 --> 00:25:23,310
Put him down!

535
00:25:23,310 --> 00:25:24,510
Step back!

536
00:25:24,510 --> 00:25:25,240
Hold the baby.

537
00:25:25,240 --> 00:25:26,240
